      • execute

        protected byte[] execute(java.sql.Connection conn)
                  throws java.sql.SQLException,
                         java.io.IOException,
                         java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException
        Execute the test element.
        参数:
        conn - a Connection
        返回:
        the result of the execute command
        抛出:
        java.sql.SQLException - if a database error occurs
        java.io.IOException - when I/O error occurs
        java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException - if the user provided incorrect query type

      • execute

        protected byte[] execute(java.sql.Connection conn,
                         SampleResult sample)
                  throws java.sql.SQLException,
                         java.io.IOException,
                         java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException
        Execute the test element. Use the sample given as argument to set time to first byte in the "latency" field of the SampleResult.
        参数:
        conn - a Connection
        sample - a SampleResult to save the latency
        返回:
        the result of the execute command
        抛出:
        java.sql.SQLException - if a database error occurs
        java.io.IOException - when I/O error occurs
        java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException - if the user provided incorrect query type

      • testStarted

        public void testStarted()

        Called just before the start of the test from the main engine thread. This is before the test elements are cloned. Note that not all the test variables will have been set up at this point.

        N.B. testStarted() and testEnded() are called from different threads.

        指定者:
        testStarted 在接口中 TestStateListener
        另请参阅:
        TestStateListener.testStarted()

      • testStarted

        public void testStarted(java.lang.String host)

        Called just before the start of the test from the main engine thread. This is before the test elements are cloned. Note that not all the test variables will have been set up at this point.

        N.B. testStarted() and testEnded() are called from different threads.

        指定者:
        testStarted 在接口中 TestStateListener
        参数:
        host - name of host
        另请参阅:
        TestStateListener.testStarted(java.lang.String)

      • testEnded

        public void testEnded()

        Called once for all threads after the end of a test. This will use the same element instances as at the start of the test.

        N.B. testStarted() and testEnded() are called from different threads.

        指定者:
        testEnded 在接口中 TestStateListener
        另请参阅:
        TestStateListener.testEnded()
